Singapore Navy Launches Second LRAD 1000RX Equipped Littoral Marine Vessel
(Courtesy of NavalToday.com)
The LMV’s represent a considerable increase in capability. They are able to operate naval helicopters, which our patrol vessels today are unable to do; they can operate UAVs (unmanned aerial vehicles) as well…and have the Long Range Acoustic Device and water cannons to deal with…maritime threats that the LMVs may encounter.
 
