Support





























LRAD 1000RX






  
Remotely Operated 
Security & Response





LRAD 1000RX
Integrated Permanent Perimeter Presence
Designed for integrated applications ranging from maritime vessels to coastal, border and port security solutions, the LRAD 1000RX can be controlled remotely across an IP network enabling system operators to create a fully functional, unmanned perimeter security solution and respond to potential threats from a safe location.
The LRAD 1000RX accepts motion commands from the LRAD controller software through a point and click interface. Simply click on a target and the RX will move to center its acoustic broadcast onto a target. A standard USB joystick (not included) can also be used to control the RX’s motion. LRAD’s easy to use controller interface enables operators to visually identify a potential threat on the live video feed, aim the LRAD and deliver a powerful warning message or deterrent tone from the safety of a command and control center. The RX’s ability to immediately interact with a potential threat remotely gives security personnel more time to assess a situation and properly escalate the use of force if necessary.
Featuring an integrated camera, high-intensity searchlight (optional) and robust, IP-addressable full pan and tilt drive for precise aiming and tracking, the LRAD 1000RX can also be integrated with radar to provide automated intruder alerts. The LRAD 1000RX reduces manpower, false alarms and deadly incidents while providing a highly effective, cost efficient, remote response security solution.


FEATURES

Remotely control all functions through TCP/IP connection
Remotely respond to threats from a safe location
Low power requirements
All-weather use
Fixed infrastructure
Easy to use – Increased coverage with single operator
Increased security coverage
Improved operational efficiency
Increased response capabilities
Safer alternative to non-lethal deterrent measures

DIRECTIONALITY, POWER EFFICIENCY & RANGE

Highly intelligible communication up to 3,000 meters
Safely communicates beyond standoff distances
Clear, long range, directional communication
When integrated with radar, creates a fully functional, automated perimeter presence





