			Company Description 
		


                LRAD Corp. engages in the development, manufacture, and trade of long range acoustic devices. Its products cater to public safety, commercial security, military, and wildlife protection applications. The company was founded by Elwood G. Norris in 1980 and is headquartered in San Diego, CA.
            




